            <lg xml:id="TK602">
<l>maṭiyai maṭiyā voḻukal kuṭiyaik </l>
<l> kuṭiyāka vēṇṭu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let those, who desire that their family may be illustrious, put away all idleness from their conduct.</l>
